data.description: You will love everything about this fantastic split floor plan home. Spacious bedrooms with carpet and wood-like tile flooring in the rest of the home.  Great curb appeal and easy to maintain landscaping in the front.  Clean slate in the backyard to landscape however you like and also offering a covered patio.  Your new kitchen boasts granite countertops, island with breakfast bar, contemporary cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and walk-in pantry.  Primary bath suite has garden tub, separate shower, private toilet room, double sink vanity, and walk-in closet.  Ideal starter home.  Perfect rental home too if you're an investor. Hurry and come take a look while you still can! Thanks for taking a look.
